---

<section class="section section--dark cta" aria-labelledby="cta-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta__inner text-center">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--color-cyan)">Start here</p>
      <h2 id="cta-heading" style="color: var(--color-white); max-width: 640px; margin-inline: auto; margin-bottom: var(--space-6)">
        Let's build your LinkedIn presence the right way.
      </h2>
      <p class="cta__sub">
        Whether you are starting from scratch, scaling an existing presence, or making your
        LinkedIn advertising work harder — we would like to understand your situation before
        recommending anything. No pitch. Just a straight conversation.
      </p>

      <div class="cta__actions">
        <a href="/contact?intent=call" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg">
          Book a 30-minute call
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--outline-white btn--lg">
          Send us a message
        </a>
        <a href="/about" class="btn btn--ghost btn--lg" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6)">
          Read how we work →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 80% at 50% 100%, rgba(0, 168, 220, 0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .cta__inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .cta__sub {
    font-size: var(--font-size-md);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
  }

  .cta__actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .cta__actions {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .cta__actions .btn {
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
